about.summary: Creates a version constraint of supported Rubies,suitable for a gemspec file

name: rb-ruby_dep
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "ruby_dep" %}
{% set version = "1.5.0" %}

package:
  name: rb-{{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://rubygems.org/downloads/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.gem
  sha256: c5bfbc7c53f9b40d287f426846d0b5765b3d0d197aca60e766b3a678129d2bb0

build:
  noarch: generic
  number: 1
  script:
    - gem install -N -l -V --norc --ignore-dependencies {{ name }}-{{ version }}.gem
    - gem unpack {{ name }}-{{ version }}.gem
  skip: {{ win }}

requirements:
  host:
    - ruby
  run:
    - ruby

test:
  commands:
    - ruby -r {{ name }} -e 'exit 0'

about:
  home: https://rubygems.org/gems/{{ name }}
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: {{ name }}-{{ version }}/LICENSE.txt
  summary: Creates a version constraint of supported Rubies,suitable for a gemspec file

  doc_url: http://www.rubydoc.info/gems/{{ name }}
  dev_url: https://github.com/e2/{{ name }}

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - sodre
